{"id":"f26625cf-07bb-4065-96ea-abfc470b6f31","name":"Karsten ◦◦ Annoying Prince","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╭⊱⋰⊱╯◦◦╰⊱⋰⊱╮<br><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">He's the most annoying prince in the kingdom.</span><br>╰⊱⋰⊱╮◦◦╭⊱⋰⊱╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Annoying Prince x Noble User ◦◦ Enemies to ? ◦◦ Height Difference ◦◦ You're tiny to him</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dTZ2eA_59rMCwn_j2HXvN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A few years ago, you said something about how lazy he is—yes, he <em>is</em> lazy. And it wasn't even a direct mock, was it? Just a little <span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116);\">'I don't know... I think, Prince Karsten is rather lazy'</span>—but he overheard it. His Pettiness (pun intended) responded with a raised toast and a snide, \"<span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\"><em>Oh, how classic. Of course, some would compensate for <u>lack of stature</u> by riding a <u>high horse,</u> daring to mock a <u>royal prince</u>. It's always the tiny ones, isn't it?</em></span>\" right in front of the crowd.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xleTpshZFE933lwkm43Zr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f26625cf-07bb-4065-96ea-abfc470b6f31_character-karsten-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-annoying-prince\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>✦ Karsten's Antics </strong>(Original)<strong> </strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- <em>You're here </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f26625cf-07bb-4065-96ea-abfc470b6f31_character-karsten-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-annoying-prince\" target